c.UIL-MEDIUM-ICON-TOGGLE-BUTTON.ua.LABEL: Enable User Menu Choices for GUIMove
c.UIL-MEDIUM-ICON-TOGGLE-BUTTON.ua.TOGGLELABEL: Enable User Menu Choices for GUIMove

g2:Structure.g2:sa.UIL-BUTTON-LABEL-VALUE: Enable User Menu Choices for GUIMove

g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT: _guimove-toggle-user-menu-choices (B: class uil-button, W: class item, D-or-W: class item) begin if (the toggle-state of B is on) then conclude that guimove-user-menu-choices-active is true else conclude that guimove-user-menu-choices-active is false; end

g2:c.RULE.g2:a.TEXT: whenever any item G is moved by the user and when there exists a uil-dialog D such that (the uil-dialog-in-use of D is true and the id of D = "guimove-item-master-dialog" and G is the-object-initiating-dialog-activity-for D) then start guimove-update-dialog-from-item (the item, D)

g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.LABEL: MOVE. . .
g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.CONDITION: (the item is not a kb-workspace) and (the workspace of the item exists and the workspace of the item is not a message-board) and guimove-user-menu-choices-active is true and the item is not a gfr-version-information-object
g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.ACTION: start uil-control-dialog-callback ("guimove-item-master-dialog", the symbol none, guimove-update-and-show-actions, the item, this window)
